    loginForm  -- HTTP request body containing attacker-controlled email
    |
    v
[STEP] UserServiceImpl.authenticateUserLogin (services/identity/src/main/java/com/crapi/service/Impl/UserServiceImpl.java:84)
    loginForm.getEmail()  -- extracted email passed from controller
    |
    v
[SINK] UserServiceImpl.authenticateUserLogin (services/identity/src/main/java/com/crapi/service/Impl/UserServiceImpl.java:101)
    >>> LOG4J_LOGGER.error("Log4j Exploit Success With Email: {}", loginForm.getEmail());
```

